            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 rounded-xl text-white text-lg shadow-md">üìÅ</div>
            <span class="text-lg">Categor√≠a</span>
            <span class="text-red-500 text-lg">*</span>
